sparql_query_raw:
To produce a SPARQL query for KG2 (Wikidata), we need to use the equivalent properties and classes. In Wikidata, the property for birth place is `P20` and the class for soccer players is `Q471167`.

Here's the SPARQL query for KG2:

`sparql`
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { 
  ?uri a <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q471167> ; 
    <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/P20> <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q143> 
  .
}
</sparql>
